description: TVCatchup lets you watch live UK TV
overview:
TVCatchup (http://TVCatchup.com) relays Live UK Freeview Television typically found on household TVs on the internet. Just some of the channels on TVCatchup, include BBC, ITV, Dave, channel 1, and channels for for children too…

Watch Live TV on your computer, mobile, iphone/ipad and Android. So whether you are at work, at home or on holiday you truly never need to miss TV again.

41 Live Freeview TV Channels on iPhone/iTouch and 30 Channels on iPad http://iphone.tvcatchup.com/ http://ipad.tvcatchup.com/

28 Live Freeview TV Channels on Android Phones and Others (More Soon) http://m.tvcatchup.com/

41 Live Freeview TV Channels on PC, Mac or Linux: http://tvcatchup.com/

41 Live Freeview TV Channels on XMBC and MCE: TVCatchup plugin for XBMC http://plugins.tvcatchup.com/~xbmc/ TVCatchup plugin for MCE http://plugins.tvcatchup.com/~mce/
